  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, how is your bank exam prep going these days? I hope it’s going well! I love learning about people’s goals. Have you tried any new study methods lately?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's going okay... but I feel stuck. I tried study group but no help. Football practice takes time, so I get frustrated. How about you, Maya? What's your hobby?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — feeling stuck is tough. Football practice sounds fun, though! I enjoy reading and sipping tea on quiet evenings. What do you like to do when you relax?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "When I relax, I watch Bengali movies or take photos. Bengali cinema has some good stories. But today, even that didn’t cheer me up much. I got frustrated because my camera broke. Bad day, you know?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I'm sorry to hear about your camera — that is a bad day! Movies can help, but I get how it's hard when they don't cheer you up. Did you try fixing it, or is it in for repair?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I tried to fix it myself, but no luck. It’s at the repair shop now. Honestly, I feel like *kotha khabo* — like nothing is going right today. Even my study plan messed up. But I need to focus, you know? Bank exam is getting closer."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I understand — when many things go wrong, it feels heavy. 'Kotha khabo' is a strong phrase! In English, we might say 'nothing is going right.' You said it well. Let’s talk about something fun — who is your favorite actor in Bengali cinema?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite actor? That’s a tough one… but I’d say Dev! He’s in so many great movies. Some people prefer Amitabh, but I like Dev’s style better. Do you watch Bengali movies, Maya? Or do you like only English films?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I watch some Bengali movies — Dev is a great choice! You said it well, \"Dev’s style.\" Small fix: we say \"I like Dev’s style better.\" You’re doing great! What’s one scene of his that you enjoy the most?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "One scene? Hmm… it’s hard to pick just one! But maybe *Bikroye* — his role there was so powerful. The way he showed pain and hope… man, it gets me every time. But enough about that — I need to check my study schedule again. Gotta get back on track. Thanks for listening, Maya."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re very welcome — and thank YOU for sharing that scene. It makes me want to watch *Bikroye*! On your study schedule — what one thing will you focus on today? Just one small step is fine."
    }
  ],
